      "role": "user",
      "content": "ok that makes sense. so i'll look for some bulging or leaks. but what if i don't see anything obvious? it's just such a weird, inconsistent noise... like it's partially working then just cutting out for no reason. could it be some kind of electrical glitch or something?",
